<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT46">
<l>vaippaṉ maṇiviḷakkā māmatiyai mālukkeṉ</l>
<l>ṟeppoḻutun kaiṉīṭṭum yāṉaiyai yeppāṭum</l>
<l>vēṭuvaḷaik kakkuṟavar villeṭukkum vēṅkaṭamē</l>
<l>nāṭuvaḷait tāṭumēl naṉṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the world dances [going] around Veṅkaṭam—</l>
<l rend="indent">where the hill-people take up bows</l>
<l rend="indent">As the hunters surround from all sides</l>
<l rend="indent">the elephant that at all times stretches out [its] trunk</l>
<l rend="indent">saying ‘I shall place the big full moon as a beautiful lamp for Māl,’</l>
<l>—[it will be] good.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
